Title: Marine Down
Plot: After a marine widow receives a call from her dead husband, the NCIS team takes on the case and has to exhume the body to deduce whether the call was a prank or not.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Erich Anderson, Richard Brooks, John Rubinstein, Carlos Sanz, Jason Brooks, Rebecca Boyd, Alan Dale, Jennifer Tighe, Pancho Demmings
